Sinatra app for Todo webapp

# Notes
  - Default view should ask to add one with an arrow pointing to the '+'
  - When a new list is created, should generate a success message
  - Each list shows the number of items in it on the main screen
  - When an item is added to the list, should generate a success message
  - When a list has at least 1 item, the complete all box should appear
    - If you click that box, it should show a confirmation box
  - Checked items become greyed out and strikethrough
  - When all list items are checked, the list title should also be grey and striked
  - If you submit an empty string for your todo, you should get an error message
    - Todos should be between 1 and 200 chars
    - Same error for empty list name